content.raw:
just noticed a compiler warning about an unused variable in the performance test:

~~~
/home/scpeters/ws_old/ignition/src/ign-physics/test/performance/ExpectData.cc:52:17: warning: unused variable ‘s’ [-Wunused-variable]
     StringData &s = data.template Get<StringData>();
                 ^
~~~

maybe we could add a small expectation that the string data isn't empty?
